@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Get Carbon Inventory KPIs - All Years
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/carbon-inventories/kpis HTTP/1.1


### Get Carbon Inventory KPIs - Specific Year (2024)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/carbon-inventories/kpis?year=2024 HTTP/1.1


### Get Carbon Inventory KPIs - Specific Year (2023)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/carbon-inventories/kpis?year=2023 HTTP/1.1
